minios-session-manager (1.1.3) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Core improvements:
    - Fix data copying reliability: use rsync to correctly handle special files
      and permissions
    - Fix export issues: ensure symbolic links point to correct targets in
      archives
    - Fix Native session handling: correct directory structure during
      import/export
    - Improve stability: better handling of mount points to prevent "device
      busy" errors
    - Improve cleanup: ensure temporary files are removed even if process is
      interrupted

  * Compatibility and dependencies:
    - Add support for running on tmpfs (RAM-based filesystems)
    - Add dependency on rsync package
    - Remove obsolete code for better maintainability

  * Localization:
    - Update translation files

 -- crims0n <crims0n@minios.dev>  Wed, 03 Dec 2025 19:48:43 +0300

